title: Internet Downlaod Manager 6.20
description:
Here Is the Internet Downlaod Manager 6.20 (Tested on windows 7) 

1 - Close/uninstall previous version of IDM

2 - Install version 6.20 build 5

3 - Copy all files(2) from ''Crack'' folder and past (replace) it in orginial installed folder (normally 
	C:Program Files (x86)Internet Download Manager or 
	C:Program FilesInternet Download Manager)

4 - Go to "Reg" folder and run reg file
Done! Enjoy!!!

Regards,
